ZH: 我每周都要花几个小时备课。
EN: I spend several hours lesson planning every week.

ZH: 老师们必须花时间备课才能给学生提供最好的教学。
EN: Teachers must invest time in lesson planning to provide the best instruction for students.

ZH: 我们需要备好明天的课程材料。
EN: We need to prepare tomorrow's lesson materials.

ZH: 老师们在备课时会参考教学大纲。
EN: Teachers refer to the curriculum when lesson planning.

ZH: 我们需要提前备课，确保课堂上一切顺利进行。
EN: We need to prepare in advance to ensure a smooth class.

